summary: AN ORDINANCE continuing, carrying over and transferring to Objects of Expenditure in the 1977 Budget of the unexpended and unencumbered balances of certain 1976 budget appropriations made from the General, Park and Recreation, Library, City-County Health, Seattle Center, City Street, Arterial City Street, Light, Water, Sewer, Engineering Department Operating, Building Department Operating, General Services Operating, Personnel Services Operating, Treasurer's Office Operating, Human Resources Operating, Community Development Operating, Arts Commission Operating, Employees' Retirement, and Model City Funds.
